snippet.title: Sonic Unleashed but it's my own fan game
snippet.description:
I have updated Sonic and The Hedgehogs.

The latest version can be found on this link:
https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1BhPI_Hx2NK3UMVQyTIpjLrPA1IhNGlWI

The Sonic Unleashed levels now have (mostly) working grind rails.

Also, here is the link for the Sonic And The Hedgehogs Discord:
https://discord.gg/2dDdmxtkGs

0:00 - Logo Screen
0:13 - Stage Select
0:21 - Windmill Isle Act 1
1:14 - Windmill Isle Act 2
5:21 - Cool Edge
8:45 - Skyscraper Scamper
12:52 - Savannah Citadel 
16:29 - Jungle Joyride
23:35 - Dragon Road

#sonic #sonicthehedgehog #grinding   #sonicfangame #unity #unity3d #fangame
